article.description: C.J. Burks had 25 points as Marshall narrowly beat IUPUI 78-73 in the first round of the CIT on Tuesday night. Jon Elmore added 22 points for the Thundering Herd.
article.headline: Burks carries Marshall over IUPUI 78-73 in CIT
article.linkText: Burks carries Marshall over IUPUI 78-73 in CIT
article.story: HUNTINGTON, W.Va. -- C.J. Burks had 25 points as Marshall narrowly beat IUPUI 78-73 in the first round of the CIT on Tuesday night. Jon Elmore added 22 points for the Thundering Herd. Taevion Kinsey had 16 points for Marshall (20-14). Camron Justice had 22 points for the Jaguars (16-17). D.J. McCall added 13 points. Elyjah Goss had 11 points. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
